<span id="freeTextContainer1359284948932782565">If you like your fantasy Rothfuss or Sanderson-style this is a great book for you. It&apos;s a meaty epic fantasy with a really strong main character. I was sucked in and definitely want to read the next one!</span>
  <span id="freeText1359284948932782565" style="display:none">If you like your fantasy Rothfuss or Sanderson-style this is a great book for you. It's a meaty epic fantasy with a really strong main character. I was sucked in and definitely want to read the next one!</span>
